{
  "stem": "8072.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they-- when we-- you know, like, lay down on the ground, they, they didn't want to be seen, SS.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want to see the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just coming closer to the prisoners, [? laying ?] the other prisoner, you know, something like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then when it's over, they start it again, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in our march, you know, it was just kind of-- gee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even remember, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we were marching for a week, or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you have shoes?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wooden shoes or something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was already-- that was already in April.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was warm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't in, in-- near-- Dachau was near Bavaria, so it wasn't as cold there then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already warmer a little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was warm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't-- I don't know exactly what the temperature was, but it was warmer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, some [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I was wearing the, the, the striped clothes, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were wearing the same striped clothes, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Marching?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was about-- it, it must have been about close to a week or something like that, three or four days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, and then when we got closer, and-- that was already close to the-- [CLEARS THROAT] --for the Germans losing the war because you could see the bombings more often, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, I don't know what day it was, and then one high-ranking German officer-- not SS, but Wehrmacht-- drove by, and he saw him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [CLEARS THROAT] --I don't know who to, whichever SS man, he talked to, and he said that not to march us anymore, not to kill us, but to leave us and turn us over to the American army, to the American Army, or whoever is there.",
      "word_count": 47
    }
  ],
